  • Method Details

    • of

      static ParameterizedTypeName of(ClassTypeName raw, ReferenceTypeName first, ReferenceTypeName... rest)
      Creates a new ParameterizedTypeName of the generic type raw whose type arguments are given by first and rest in order.

      Typical usage: 

       // List<Path>
 ParameterizedTypeName.of(
   ClassTypeName.of(List.class),
   ClassTypeName.of(Path.class)
 )

 // Map<String, E>
 ParameterizedTypeName.of(
   ClassTypeName.of(Map.class),
   ClassTypeName.of(String.class),
   TypeVariableName.of("E")
 )

 // Future<List<LocalDate>>
 ParameterizedTypeName.of(
   ClassTypeName.of(Future.class),
   ParameterizedTypeName.of(
     ClassTypeName.of(List.class),
     ClassTypeName.of(LocalDate.class)
   )
 )
      Parameters:
      raw - the generic type
      first - the first type argument
      rest - the remaining type arguments
      Returns:
      a newly constructed ParameterizedTypeName instance
